Transformation Notes:
<work> rdawo:P10256 <tConcept(field)> . // has subject; complete heading
<tConcept(field)> skos:prefLabel "stripEndStop(concatenateOA($a, $b, $c, $d, $f, $j, $q, $u, $t, $f, $g, $h, $k, $l, $m, $n, $o, $p, $r, $s, $v, $x, $y, $z))"
<tConcept(field)> skos:inScheme <tScheme(field)> . // has scheme of nomen
Scheme is in indicator 2 or $2 if the second indicator is 7

MARCInd1Label: Type of personal name entry element
Transformation Notes:
<work> rdawo:P10261 <personS> . // has subject person
<personS> rdaao:P50411 <nomenP> . // has authorized access point for person; if ind2=4 (no source), then use datatype property and nomen string
<nomenP> rdand:P80068 “stripEndStop(concatenateOA($a, $b, $c, $d, $j, $q $u))” . // has nomen string; OA = in order of appearance
<nomenP> rdano:P80069 <tScheme(600)> . // has scheme of nomen; no statement if ind2=4
